<lb n="0508b13"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0508b14"/>
<lb n="0508b15"/><head type="no">No. 118 [No. 99(1077), No. 100(16), No.
<lb n="0508b16"/>125(38.6), Nos. 119-120]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0508b17"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title>佛說<note n="0508003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鴦掘摩＝鴦崛摩【三】</note><note n="0508003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鴦掘摩＝鴦崛摩【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508003"><lem>鴦掘摩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">鴦崛摩</rdg></app>經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0508b18"/>
<lb n="0508b19"/><byline type="Translator">西晉<note n="0508004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔月氏國〕－【三】</note><note n="0508004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔月氏國〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508004"><lem>月氏國</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0508005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三藏＋（法師）【三】</note><note n="0508005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三藏＋（法師）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508005"><lem>三藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">三藏法師</rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb n="0508b20"/><p>聞如是。一時佛遊舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。與
<lb n="0508b21"/>大比丘五百眾俱。舍衛城中有異梵志。博綜
<lb n="0508b22"/>三經無所疑滯。具暢五典所問即對。精生講
<lb n="0508b23"/>肆莫不稟仰。國老諮<note n="0508006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諏＝趣【三】</note><note n="0508006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諏＝趣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508006"><lem>諏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">趣</rdg></app>群儒宗焉。門徒濟濟
<lb n="0508b24"/>有五百人。上首弟子名<note n="0508007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鴦掘摩＝鴦崛摩【明】＊</note><app n="0508007"><lem>鴦掘摩</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">鴦崛摩</rdg></app><note n="0508008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔晉曰指鬘〕－【明】</note><app n="0508008"><lem><note place="inline">晉曰指鬘</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。儀幹剛
<lb n="0508b25"/>猛力超壯士。手能接飛走先奔馬。聰慧才辯
<lb n="0508b26"/>志性和雅。安詳敏達一無疑礙。色像第一師
<lb n="0508b27"/>所嘉異。<note n="0508009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">室主＝室生【三】</note><note n="0508009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">室主＝室生【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508009"><lem>室主</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">室生</rdg></app>欽敬候夫出處。往造指鬘而謂
<lb n="0508b28"/>之曰。觀爾顏彩有堂堂之容。推步年齒相覺
<lb n="0508b29"/>不殊。寧可同歡接所娛乎。指鬘聞之慞惶怖
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0118.0508c" n="0508c"/>
<lb n="0508c01"/>懼。毛衣起&CB00594;跪而答曰。夫人比母師則當父。
<lb n="0508c02"/>猥垂斯教<note n="0508010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">儀＝義【三】</note><note n="0508010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">儀＝義【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508010"><lem>儀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">義</rdg></app>不敢許。心所不甘甚非法也。師
<lb n="0508c03"/>婦又曰。飢者與食渴給水漿有何非法。寒施
<lb n="0508c04"/>溫衣熱惠清涼有何非法。裸露復之危厄救
<lb n="0508c05"/>之有何非法。指鬘答曰。赴趣患急<note n="0508011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寬＝救【三】</note><note n="0508011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寬＝救【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508011"><lem>寬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">救</rdg></app>濟窮
<lb n="0508c06"/>頓實無非法。夫人母也。師之所重。隨婬著色
<lb n="0508c07"/>慢犯非宜。如蛇<note n="0508012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蝘＝繳【宋】，&CB04825;【元】【明】</note><note n="0508012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蝘＝繳【宋】，＝&CB04825;【元】【明】</note><app n="0508012"><lem>蝘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">繳</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB04825;</rdg></app>體服毒<note n="0508013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">褒＝喪身【三】</note><note n="0508013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">褒＝喪身【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508013"><lem>褒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">喪身</rdg></app>。師室聞之即
<lb n="0508c08"/>懷<note n="0508014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">愧＝媿【三】</note><note n="0508014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">愧＝媿【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508014"><lem>愧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">媿</rdg></app>恨。歸自總<note n="0508015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滅＝搣摧【三】</note><note n="0508015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滅＝搣摧【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508015"><lem>滅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">搣摧</rdg></app>裂衣裳。&CB00614;金黃面佯愁
<lb n="0508c09"/>委臥。時夫行還。問曰。何故有何不善。誰相
<lb n="0508c10"/><note n="0508016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嬲＝嬈【三】</note><note n="0508016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嬲＝嬈【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508016"><lem>嬲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">嬈</rdg></app>觸。室人譖曰。君常所歎聰慧弟子。柔仁
<lb n="0508c11"/>貞潔履行無闕。君旦不在來<note n="0508017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝相【三】</note><note n="0508017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＝相【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508017"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">相</rdg></app>牽掣。欲肆
<lb n="0508c12"/>逆慢妾不順從。而被<note n="0508018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陵＝凌【三】</note><note n="0508018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陵＝凌【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508018"><lem>陵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">凌</rdg></app>侮摧<note n="0508019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捽＝碎【三】</note><note n="0508019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捽＝碎【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508019"><lem>捽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">碎</rdg></app>委頓。是以
<lb n="0508c13"/>受辱不能自起。師聞悵然意懷盛怒。欲加楚
<lb n="0508c14"/>罰掠治姦暴。慮之雄霸非力所伏。退欲靜默
<lb n="0508c15"/>深惟不道。穢染閨閤上下失<note n="0508020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">序＝緒【三】</note><note n="0508020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">序＝緒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508020"><lem>序</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">緒</rdg></app>。進退沈吟將
<lb n="0508c16"/>如之何。乃<note n="0508021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咿＝依【宋】，伊【元】【明】</note><note n="0508021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">咿＝依【宋】，＝伊【元】【明】</note><app n="0508021"><lem>咿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">依</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">伊</rdg></app>悒歎曰。當微改常倒教而教。
<lb n="0508c17"/>教使殺人限至于百。各貫一指以鬘其額。殺
<lb n="0508c18"/>人之罪罪莫大焉。不加楚酷必就辜戮。現受
<lb n="0508c19"/>危沒<note n="0508022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沒＝死【三】</note><note n="0508022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沒＝死【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508022"><lem>沒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">死</rdg></app>墮地獄。不可釋<note n="0508023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔置〕－【三】</note><note n="0508023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔置〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508023"><lem>置</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>縱使<note n="0508024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滋＝茲【三】</note><note n="0508024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滋＝茲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508024"><lem>滋</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">茲</rdg></app>甚也。</p>
<lb n="0508c20"/><p>於是師命指鬘而<note n="0508025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">告＋（之）【三】</note><note n="0508025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508025"><lem>告</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">告之</rdg></app>曰。卿之聰慧所學周密。
<lb n="0508c21"/><note n="0508026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">升＝計昇【三】</note><note n="0508026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">升＝計昇【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508026"><lem>升</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">計昇</rdg></app>堂入室精生無首。唯之一藝未施行耳。
<lb n="0508c22"/>指鬘進曰。願聞所告。師曰。欲速成者宜執
<lb n="0508c23"/>利劍。晨於四衢躬殺百人。人取一指以為傅
<lb n="0508c24"/>飾。至于日中使百指滿。設勤奉遵。則道德
<lb n="0508c25"/>備矣。便以&CB00669;授。指鬘受劍聞告愕懼。心懷
<lb n="0508c26"/>愁慼。設違教旨非孝弟子。順而行之畏陷失
<lb n="0508c27"/>理。奉劍而退垂淚言曰。淨修梵行則梵志法。
<lb n="0508c28"/>孝養父母則梵志法。修為眾善則梵志法。不
<lb n="0508c29"/><note n="0508027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">邪＝矯【三】</note><note n="0508027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">邪＝矯【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508027"><lem>邪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">矯</rdg></app>正歸則梵志法。柔和<note n="0508028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仁惠＝仁慧【三】</note><note n="0508028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">仁惠＝仁慧【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508028"><lem>仁惠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">仁慧</rdg></app>則梵志法。弘
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0118.0509a" n="0509a"/>
<lb n="0509a01"/>慈四等則梵志。法得五神通則梵志法。超上
<lb n="0509a02"/>梵天則梵志法。今暴伐殺非法失理。躊躇懊
<lb n="0509a03"/>惱當如之何。即詣<note n="0509001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">前＝叢【三】</note><note n="0509001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前＝叢【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509001"><lem>前</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">叢</rdg></app>樹四衢路側。悲怒<note n="0509002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">激＝憿【三】</note><note n="0509002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">激＝憿【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509002"><lem>激</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">憿</rdg></app>
<lb n="0509a04"/>憤惡鬼助禍。耗亂其心瞋目噴吒。四顧遠視
<lb n="0509a05"/>如鬼師子。如虎<note n="0509003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">狼＝猛【三】</note><note n="0509003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狼＝猛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509003"><lem>狼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">猛</rdg></app>獸跳騰馳踊。色貌可畏
<lb n="0509a06"/>行者四集。悉當趣城即奮長劍多所殺害。莫
<lb n="0509a07"/>不迸怖值無遺脫。去來往返而無覺者。無數
<lb n="0509a08"/>之眾稱怨悲叫。入<note n="0509004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">趣＝赴【三】</note><note n="0509004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">趣＝赴【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509004"><lem>趣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">赴</rdg></app>王宮告有逆賊。遮截要
<lb n="0509a09"/>路害人不少。唯願<note n="0509005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天王＝大王【三】</note><note n="0509005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天王＝大王【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509005"><lem>天王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">大王</rdg></app>。為民除患。時諸比
<lb n="0509a10"/>丘入城分衛見諸告者。恐怖如是。分衛還出
<lb n="0509a11"/>飯食畢訖。往詣佛所稽首足下白世尊曰。見
<lb n="0509a12"/>國人眾詣王宮門。<note n="0509006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">告＋（有）【三】</note><note n="0509006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告＋（有）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509006"><lem>告</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">告有</rdg></app>大逆賊名曰指鬘。手執
<lb n="0509a13"/>利劍多所危害。體掌污血路無行人。</p>
<lb n="0509a14"/><p>爾時世尊告諸比丘。汝等且止。吾往救之。佛
<lb n="0509a15"/>從坐起尋到其所。道逢&CB00034;牧荷負載乘。佃居
<lb n="0509a16"/><note n="0509007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">民眾＝眾民【三】</note><note n="0509007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">民眾＝眾民【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509007"><lem>民眾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">眾民</rdg></app>白世尊曰。大聖所湊<note n="0509008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勿＝無【三】</note><note n="0509008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勿＝無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509008"><lem>勿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>由斯路。前有
<lb n="0509a17"/>逆賊四徼道斷。<note n="0509009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">取＝所【三】</note><note n="0509009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">取＝所【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509009"><lem>取</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">所</rdg></app>殺狼藉唯改所從。又且獨
<lb n="0509a18"/>步<note n="0509010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＋（有）【三】</note><note n="0509010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無＋（有）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509010"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">無有</rdg></app>侍衛故也。世尊告曰。設使三界盡為寇
<lb n="0509a19"/>虜吾不省錄。況一賊乎。指鬘之母怪子不歸。
<lb n="0509a20"/>時至不食懼必當飢。齎餉出城就<note n="0509011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">而＝如【三】</note><note n="0509011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而＝如【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509011"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">如</rdg></app>餉之日
<lb n="0509a21"/><note n="0509012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲向＝向欲【三】</note><note n="0509012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲向＝向欲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509012"><lem>欲向</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">向欲</rdg></app>中百指未滿。恐日移昳道業不具。欲還
<lb n="0509a22"/>害母以充其數。佛念指鬘若害母者。在不中
<lb n="0509a23"/>止罪不可救。佛便忽然住立其前。時<app type="＊" source="0508007"><lem>鴦掘摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">鴦崛摩</rdg></app>
<lb n="0509a24"/>見佛捨母。如師子步往迎世尊。心自念言。十
<lb n="0509a25"/>人百人見我馳迸<note n="0509013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝莫【三】</note><note n="0509013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＝莫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509013"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">莫</rdg></app>敢當也。吾常奮威縱橫
<lb n="0509a26"/>自恣。況此沙門獨身<note n="0509014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">而至＝如此【三】</note><note n="0509014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而至＝如此【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509014"><lem>而至</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">如此</rdg></app>。<note n="0509015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">今＝當【明】</note><app n="0509015"><lem>今</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">當</rdg></app>我規圖必勦
<lb n="0509a27"/>其命。<note n="0509016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＝便【三】</note><note n="0509016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即＝便【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509016"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">便</rdg></app>執劍趣佛不能自前竭力奔走亦不
<lb n="0509a28"/>能到則心念曰。我跳度江河解諸繫縛。<note n="0509017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">投＝捉【三】</note><note n="0509017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">投＝捉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509017"><lem>投</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">捉</rdg></app>捭
<lb n="0509a29"/>勇猛曾無匹敵。重關固塞無不開<note n="0509018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">闔＝闢【三】</note><note n="0509018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">闔＝闢【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509018"><lem>闔</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">闢</rdg></app>。而此沙
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0118.0509b" n="0509b"/>
<lb n="0509b01"/>門徐步<note n="0509019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">裁＝纔【三】</note><note n="0509019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">裁＝纔【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509019"><lem>裁</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">纔</rdg></app>動我走不及。殫盡威勢永不摩近。
<lb n="0509b02"/>指鬘謂佛。沙門且止。佛告逆賊。吾止<note n="0509020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【三】＊</note><note n="0509020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝以【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0509020"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>來
<lb n="0509b03"/>其日久矣。但汝未止。時<app type="＊" source="0508007"><lem>鴦掘摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">鴦崛摩</rdg></app>遙以偈頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0509b04"/><lg><l>寂志語何謂</l><l>自云已停跱</l>
<lb n="0509b05"/><l>斯言何所趣</l><l>以我為不止</l>
<lb n="0509b06"/><l>今佛云何立</l><l>謂身行不住</l>
<lb n="0509b07"/><l>反以我若茲</l><l>願說解此義</l></lg>
<lb n="0509b08"/><p>於是世尊為指鬘頌偈。而告之曰。</p>
<lb n="0509b09"/><lg><l>指鬘聽佛住</l><l>世尊<note n="0509021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">除君過＝降群愚【三】</note><note n="0509021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">除君過＝降群愚【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509021"><lem>除君過</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">降群愚</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0509b10"/><l>汝走無<note n="0509022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＝知【三】</note><note n="0509022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智＝知【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509022"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">知</rdg></app>想</l><l>吾定爾不止</l>
<lb n="0509b11"/><l>吾安住三脫</l><l>樂法修梵行</l>
<lb n="0509b12"/><l>汝獨驅<note n="0509023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">癡＝疑【三】</note><note n="0509023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">癡＝疑【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509023"><lem>癡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">疑</rdg></app>想</l><l>懷害今<note n="0509024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">未＝不【三】</note><note n="0509024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未＝不【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509024"><lem>未</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">不</rdg></app>止</l>
<lb n="0509b13"/><l>大聖無極慧</l><l><note n="0509025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">讚＝講【三】</note><note n="0509025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">讚＝講【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509025"><lem>讚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">講</rdg></app>寂於四衢</l>
<lb n="0509b14"/><l>尋聞所說罪</l><l>聽<note n="0509026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">釆詠＝採訓【三】</note><note n="0509026" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.say">采</lem><rdg wit="【大】">釆</rdg></app>詠＝採訓【宋】【元】【明】<app><lem resp="CBETA.say" cf1="K19p599b03">，＝釆詠【麗】</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note><app n="0509026"><lem>采詠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">採訓</rdg><rdg wit="【麗】" resp="CBETA.say" cf1="K19p599b03">釆詠</rdg></app>法義</l></lg>
<lb n="0509b15"/><p>於是指鬘心<note n="0509027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＝自【明】</note><app n="0509027"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">自</rdg></app>開悟。棄劍稽首自投于地。唯
<lb n="0509b16"/>願世尊。恕我迷謬。興害集指念欲見道。僥賴
<lb n="0509b17"/>慈化乞原罪舋。垂哀接濟得使出家受成就
<lb n="0509b18"/>戒。佛則授之即為沙門。</p>
<lb n="0509b19"/><p>爾時世尊威神巍巍。智慧<note n="0509028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光明＝光光【三】</note><note n="0509028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">光明＝光光【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509028"><lem>光明</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">光光</rdg></app>結<note n="0509029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">加＝跏【三】</note><note n="0509029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">加＝跏【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509029"><lem>加</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">跏</rdg></app>趺坐。
<lb n="0509b20"/>賢者指鬘翼從左右。還至祇樹給孤獨園。指
<lb n="0509b21"/>鬘蒙化眾祐所信。諸<note n="0509030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尊＝賢【三】</note><note n="0509030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尊＝賢【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509030"><lem>尊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">賢</rdg></app>弟子亦共攝持。其族
<lb n="0509b22"/>姓子。下鬚髮者<note n="0509031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則＝即【三】</note><note n="0509031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則＝即【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509031"><lem>則</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">即</rdg></app><note n="0509032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">被＝披【宋】【元】</note><app n="0509032"><lem>被</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">披</rdg></app>法服。以家之信捨家
<lb n="0509b23"/>為道。具足究竟無上梵行。得六通證生死已
<lb n="0509b24"/>斷。稱舉<note n="0509033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淨＝清【三】</note><note n="0509033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淨＝清【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509033"><lem>淨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">清</rdg></app>德所作已辦。解名色本即得應
<lb n="0509b25"/>真。</p>
<lb n="0509b26"/><p>時王<note n="0509034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波私匿＝波斯匿【三】</note><note n="0509034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">波私匿＝波斯匿【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509034"><lem>波私匿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">波斯匿</rdg></app><note n="0509035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔晉號和悅〕－【三】</note><note n="0509035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔晉號和悅〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509035"><lem><note place="inline">晉號和悅</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。與四部眾象馬步騎。嚴駕
<lb n="0509b27"/>出征欲討穢逆。<note n="0509036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝王【三】</note><note n="0509036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其＝王【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509036"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">王</rdg></app>身疲弊而被塵土。過詣佛
<lb n="0509b28"/>所稽首足下。佛問。王曰。從何所來身被塵土。
<lb n="0509b29"/>王白佛言。唯然世尊。有大逆賊名<app type="＊" source="0508007"><lem>鴦掘摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">鴦崛摩</rdg></app>。
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0118.0509c" n="0509c"/>
<lb n="0509c01"/>兇暴懷害斷四徼道。手執嚴刃傷殺人民。今
<lb n="0509c02"/>故<note n="0509037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">匡＝總【三】</note><note n="0509037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">匡＝總【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509037"><lem>匡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">總</rdg></app>勒四部之眾欲出討捕。是時指鬘在於
<lb n="0509c03"/>會中。去佛不遠。佛告王曰。指鬘在此。已除鬚
<lb n="0509c04"/>髮今為比丘。本<note n="0509038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">與＝舉【三】</note><note n="0509038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">與＝舉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509038"><lem>與</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">舉</rdg></app>云何。王白佛言。已志于
<lb n="0509c05"/>道無如之何。當盡形壽給其衣食臥起床<note n="0509039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＝座【明】</note><app n="0509039"><lem>坐</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">座</rdg></app>
<lb n="0509c06"/>病瘦醫藥。又問世尊。唯然大聖。<note n="0509040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">凶＝兇【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0509040"><lem>凶</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">兇</rdg></app>害逆人
<lb n="0509c07"/>焉得至道履行寂義乎。今為安在。佛告王曰。
<lb n="0509c08"/>近在斯坐。王遙見之。心即懷懼衣毛為&CB00594;。佛
<lb n="0509c09"/>言。大王。莫恐莫懅。今以仁賢無復逆意。王
<lb n="0509c10"/>造禮之謂曰。賢者。是指鬘乎。答曰。是也。
<lb n="0509c11"/>王又問曰。仁姓為何。曰。奇角<note n="0509041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">氏＋（也）【三】</note><note n="0509041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">氏＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509041"><lem>氏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">氏也</rdg></app>。又<note n="0509042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">問＋（曰）【三】</note><note n="0509042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">問＋（曰）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509042"><lem>問</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">問曰</rdg></app>。何
<lb n="0509c12"/>謂奇角氏。曰父本姓。王曰。唯奇角子受吾供
<lb n="0509c13"/>養。衣食床臥病瘦醫藥各盡形壽。即然所供。
<lb n="0509c14"/>王<note n="0509043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝唯【三】</note><note n="0509043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝唯【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509043"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app>獲許稽首辭還。歎世尊曰。能調諸不
<lb n="0509c15"/>調。能成諸未成。安住垂大慈。無所不開<note n="0509044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＝導【三】</note><note n="0509044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道＝導【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509044"><lem>道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">導</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0509c16"/>消伏患逆使充法會。亦令&CB00848;庶逮斯調定。我
<lb n="0509c17"/>國多事意欲請退。佛告。便去從<note n="0509045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">志＝心【三】</note><note n="0509045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">志＝心【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509045"><lem>志</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">心</rdg></app>所奉。王
<lb n="0509c18"/>禮佛足稽首而歸。</p>
<lb n="0509c19"/><p>爾時賢者指鬘。處於閑居服五納衣。明旦持
<lb n="0509c20"/>&CB00425;入舍衛城普行分衛。見有諸家懷妊女人。
<lb n="0509c21"/>月滿產難心歸怙之。問指鬘曰。欲何至趣唯
<lb n="0509c22"/>蒙救濟。指鬘得供出城食畢。澡竟去器獨坐
<lb n="0509c23"/>加敬。詣佛稽首白世尊曰。我朝晨旦著衣持
<lb n="0509c24"/>&CB00425;入城分衛。見有女人臨月欲產。產難恐懼
<lb n="0509c25"/>求見<note n="0509046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">救＝擁【三】</note><note n="0509046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">救＝擁【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509046"><lem>救</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">擁</rdg></app>護。佛告指鬘。汝便速往謂女人曰。
<lb n="0509c26"/>如指鬘言至誠不虛。從生<app type="＊" source="0509020"><lem>已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>來未<note n="0509047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嘗＝曾【三】</note><note n="0509047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嘗＝曾【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509047"><lem>嘗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">曾</rdg></app>殺生。
<lb n="0509c27"/>審如是者。姊當尋<note n="0509048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝產【三】</note><note n="0509048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝產【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509048"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">產</rdg></app>安隱無患。指鬘白佛。
<lb n="0509c28"/>我作眾罪不可稱計。發九十九人一不滿百。
<lb n="0509c29"/>而發此言豈非兩舌乎。世尊告曰。前生異世
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0118.0510a" n="0510a"/>
<lb n="0510a01"/>今生不同。是則至誠不為妄語。<note n="0510001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＝汝【三】</note><note n="0510001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如＝汝【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510001"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">汝</rdg></app>斯用時救
<lb n="0510a02"/>彼女厄。即奉聖旨往到女<note n="0510002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所＝許【宋】</note><app n="0510002"><lem>所</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">許</rdg></app>。如佛言曰。如
<lb n="0510a03"/>我至誠所言不虛。從生<note n="0510003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【宋】【元】</note><app n="0510003"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>來未曾殺生。審
<lb n="0510a04"/>如是者。當令大姊安隱在產。所言未竟女尋
<lb n="0510a05"/><note n="0510004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娩＝免【三】</note><note n="0510004" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">&CB01661;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">娩</rdg></app>＝免【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510004"><lem>&CB01661;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">免</rdg></app>軀兒亦獲安。</p>
<lb n="0510a06"/><p>爾時指鬘入舍衛城。群小童黻見之分衛。或
<lb n="0510a07"/>瓦石擲或以箭射。或刀斫刺或杖捶擊。賢者
<lb n="0510a08"/>指鬘。破頭傷體衣服<note n="0510005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">破裂＝破碎【三】</note><note n="0510005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">破裂＝破碎【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510005"><lem>破裂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">破碎</rdg></app><note n="0510006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">還＝甘【三】</note><note n="0510006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">還＝甘【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510006"><lem>還</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">甘</rdg></app>詣佛所稽首
<lb n="0510a09"/><note n="0510007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">足下起於佛前＝禮畢而歎【三】</note><note n="0510007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">足下起於佛前＝禮畢而歎【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510007"><lem>足下起於佛前</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">禮畢而歎</rdg></app>頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0510a10"/><lg><l>我前本為賊</l><l>指鬘名普聞</l>
<lb n="0510a11"/><l>大淵以枯竭</l><l>則歸命正覺</l>
<lb n="0510a12"/><l>斯以<note n="0510008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">成＝戒【三】</note><note n="0510008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">成＝戒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510008"><lem>成</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">戒</rdg></app>忍辱</l><l>逮佛開化眾</l>
<lb n="0510a13"/><l>聽經常以時</l><l>是故無躓礙</l>
<lb n="0510a14"/><l>今<app type="＊" source="0509020"><lem>已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>歸命佛</l><l>受真諦法戒</l>
<lb n="0510a15"/><l>逮得三通達</l><l>則順諸佛教</l>
<lb n="0510a16"/><l>昔暴懷兇毒</l><l>多傷眾類命</l>
<lb n="0510a17"/><l>雖古多所危</l><l>吾今名無害</l>
<lb n="0510a18"/><l>身口所犯過</l><l>志懷殺害心</l>
<lb n="0510a19"/><l>其不危他餘</l><l>未曾遭諸厄</l>
<lb n="0510a20"/><l>又復無過去</l><l><note n="0510009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持其＝值母【三】</note><note n="0510009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">持其＝值母【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510009"><lem>持其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">值母</rdg></app>法寂然</l>
<lb n="0510a21"/><l>應受<app type="＊" source="0509040"><lem>凶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">兇</rdg></app>暴名</l><l>自調成仁賢</l>
<lb n="0510a22"/><l>以才一調定</l><l>如鉤調諸象</l>
<lb n="0510a23"/><l>如來成就我</l><l>無劍亦無杖</l>
<lb n="0510a24"/><l>其前為放逸</l><l>然後能自制</l>
<lb n="0510a25"/><l>彼明炤於世</l><l><note n="0510010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">由＝猶【三】＊</note><note n="0510010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">由＝猶【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0510010"><lem>由</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">猶</rdg></app>日出於雲</l>
<lb n="0510a26"/><l>假使犯眾惡</l><l>不斷眾<note n="0510011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善德＝菩提【三】</note><note n="0510011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善德＝菩提【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510011"><lem>善德</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">菩提</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0510a27"/><l>彼明炤於世</l><l><app type="＊" source="0510010"><lem>由</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">猶</rdg></app>雲消日出</l>
<lb n="0510a28"/><l>若新學比丘</l><l>勤修於佛教</l>
<lb n="0510a29"/><l>其明炤於世</l><l>如月盛滿時</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0118.0510b" n="0510b"/>
<lb n="0510b01"/><l>其有犯眾罪</l><l>當歸於<note n="0510012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡道＝惡趣【三】</note><note n="0510012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惡道＝惡趣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510012"><lem>惡道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">惡趣</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0510b02"/><l>不復難諸患</l><l><note n="0510013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">服＝飲【三】</note><note n="0510013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">服＝飲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510013"><lem>服</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">飲</rdg></app>食無所著</l>
<lb n="0510b03"/><l>亦不求於生</l><l>未曾<note n="0510014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">會德＝貪惡【三】</note><note n="0510014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">會德＝貪惡【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510014"><lem>會德</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">貪惡</rdg></app>死</l>
<lb n="0510b04"/><l>唯須待時日</l><l>心常志於定</l>
<lb n="0510b05"/><l>如是<app type="＊" source="0508007"><lem>鴦掘摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">鴦崛摩</rdg></app></l><l>已得成羅漢</l>
<lb n="0510b06"/><l>在佛世尊前</l><l>口自頌斯偈</l></lg>
<lb n="0510b07"/><p>佛說如是。賢者指鬘及諸比丘眾。聞經歡喜
<lb n="0510b08"/><note n="0510015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔奉行〕－【三】</note><note n="0510015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔奉行〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510015"><lem>奉行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0510b09"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說<app type="＊" source="0508007"><lem>鴦掘摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">鴦崛摩</rdg></app>經</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>